{"tid":1908001,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[鋼琴JJ]有關用「FACE」記5線譜note位置","createTime":"2020-03-03T03:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T10:49:16.000Z","uid":111322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5c2942bac9de42f464be370193e9bda7da2c582d","tid":1908001,"uid":111322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:31:38.000Z","msg":"當學咗十幾年鋼琴<br />\n仲係咪會本能地用呢個方法搵note？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申學咗一年 仲係用緊 但會否有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4326abf837e172123a1335b837d4b05f5da99e9b","tid":1908001,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:32:50.000Z","msg":"彈得多自然唔洗"},{"pid":"05a69c7764ba657b37d64094a30ff62693e1fc9f","tid":1908001,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:39:02.000Z","msg":"有音感<br />\n好少睇譜<br />\n連咩key啲flat sharp<br />\n都要慢慢數"},{"pid":"dc5a9377f78be77ea3d07a4bad539454717f6dcb","tid":1908001,"uid":200895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:41:14.000Z","msg":"通常高音記一個位，eg A4 ，低音記一個位，eg C2<br />\n<br />\n如果唔記得就搵鉛筆寫個音名係上面，有sharp, flat唔記得彈咪畫個（#, b）係音上面，寫下寫下就記得。<br />\n寫野其實好正常，因為多謝玩緊音樂個腦都好難轉得到咁多野。<br />\n<br />\n數音可以一行一行咁數，eg , C , E ,G , B ,快好多<br />\n<br />\n唔使死記，用多啲就識"},{"pid":"95c84935cec7bc9b0af58d98ad378652a68570cc","tid":1908001,"uid":200895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05a69c7764ba657b37d64094a30ff62693e1fc9f","tid":1908001,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:39:02.000Z","msg":"有音感<br />\n好少睇譜<br />\n連咩key啲flat sharp<br />\n都要慢慢數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:52:04.000Z","msg":"Key 可以用 睇flat , sharp咁就快睇到 或者用 circle of fifth<br />\n<br />\nFlat 既major 可睇排尾二既flat就知乜major （除一個flat就係F major)<br />\n<br />\nEg1. 有 Bb Eb Ab &mdash;-&gt; Eb major<br />\nEg.2 有 Bb Eb Ab Db Gb Cb &mdash;&gt;Gb major<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啲flat 既關係係perfect 4th interval<br />\n<br />\nSharp就係睇最後一個# 既上一格，因為最後一個sharp既位一定係 ti ( so fa name 入面個）<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\nF# &mdash;&gt; G major<br />\nF# C# G# D# &mdash;&gt; E major<br />\n<br />\nSharp既關係係 perfect 5th interval<br />\n<br />\n至於minor 移落兩格 （精準啲係 minor 3rd lower)<br />\n<br />\n所以 C major &mdash;&gt; A minor<br />\n          G major &mdash;&gt; E minor<br />\n<br />\nHarmonic #7<br />\nMelodic 上行 #6 #7 下行咩都唔使加<br />\nNatural minor 咩都唔使加"},{"pid":"c3d6b2917d3cc32fffd4579b70eb665163a2c03d","tid":1908001,"uid":235986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T00:59:07.000Z","msg":"一樣記位置好難 有時要手寫<br />\n同埋視譜超慢"},{"pid":"ca05e2bd575013af3392309762e7d05c96325f35","tid":1908001,"uid":64457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c2942bac9de42f464be370193e9bda7da2c582d","tid":1908001,"uid":111322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:31:38.000Z","msg":"當學咗十幾年鋼琴<br />\n仲係咪會本能地用呢個方法搵note？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申學咗一年 仲係用緊 但會否有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T21:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598ae13d31e7e4c7f888a9f8147b070ca1d97ae5","tid":1908001,"uid":111322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca05e2bd575013af3392309762e7d05c96325f35","tid":1908001,"uid":64457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c2942bac9de42f464be370193e9bda7da2c582d","tid":1908001,"uid":111322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:31:38.000Z","msg":"當學咗十幾年鋼琴<br />\n仲係咪會本能地用呢個方法搵note？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申學咗一年 仲係用緊 但會否有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T21:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T10:49:16.000Z","msg":"完美解決我嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />